Big Vic officially unveiled in Nairobi as a UN Habitat brand ambassador.He is a good coach on and off the pitch...always willing to help you, says Montreal midfielder in Nairobi. Harambee Stars captain Victor Wanyama says he is happy to work under Arsenal’s legend Thierry Henry at Montreal Impact in Canada, as the Frenchman knows how to get the best from his players. 

Wanyama joined Montreal Impact in March 2020 on a three-year contract from English Premier League side Tottenham Hotspur in a free transfer. 



