Montreal Impact play in the Eastern Conference of the MLS. 

Wanyama was speaking on the side-line of  a ceremony where he was unveiled as a brand ambassador for UN Habitat in Nairobi. 

 “I have got a good relationship with Thierry. He is a good coach on and off the pitch. He is always willing to help you.” 

In October last year, Henry was captured blasting Wanyama and his teammates in their 3-2 league defeat to New England Revolution. 

“Mason was there Victor. No, don’t scream. Mason was there! Mason, tell him you were there alone,” Henry told Wanyama on the touchline of the match. 

Henry joined Montreal Impact on a two-year contract in November 2019 and guided the club to a ninth place finish last season. 



