“For me, it has been my dream to one day give back to the community and try and improve what I did not have when I was growing. 

“That (football academy) is the biggest thing we lacked here. To have that facility and the same system that they have in Europe here will make a big difference,” said Wanyama. He called on corporate organastions to join him in the initiative. 

